Have you ever felt that urge to yell “MY PAYCHECK IS JUST NOT ENOUGH…WHAT SHOULD I DO TO MAKE MORE MONEY” till your lungs burst out?

I know, I can feel your pain and frustration. I went through this exact same frustration when I used to work for a corporate company.

Worked 6 days a week and the amount I got, usually didn’t even make it till the month end and then I used to borrow money from my parents
